User stories for Forkify app

#1. As the users, I want to search for the recipes, so that I can find new ideas
for meals 

#2: #1. As the users, I want to be able to update the number of servings, so that I can cook a meal for different number of people

#3. TAs the users, I want to bookmark the recipes, so that I
can review them

#4. As the users, I want to create my own recipes, so that I can have them own organized in the same app

#5. As the users, I want to be able to see my bookmarks and my own recipes when I leave the app and come back later, so that I can close the app saely after cooking